1. *Slučaj* odlučuje o sudbini ljudi. (The case decides the fate of people.)
2. Oni nisu razmišljali o *slučaju* u kontekstu obične situacije. (They did not think about the case in the context of an ordinary situation.)
3. Oni su se konsultovali sa advokatom kako bi preduzeli sve korake u *slučaju*. (They consulted with a lawyer to take all steps in the case.)
4. *Slučaj* je završen u roku od dve nedelje. (The case was completed within two weeks.)
5. On je preuzeo svoje mesto u *slučaju*. (He took his place in the case.)